result.title: Codability training contest
result.content:
Hello everyone!

We are glad to announce that the first training contest for Codabiltiy students is going to be held on Wednesday, 20th September at 6 pm. You are all invited to participate.

This contest was prepared particularly by Mariam Jameed. Special thanks for our amazing coach Light for helping in contest preparations and for me.

There are 10 problems with 3:30 hours to solve them. A special prize will be given to the winner of the contest!

Have fun and good luck for all of you! :D

UPD: For some reasons, you are not allowed to participate as teams.

UPD: The contest starts in 20 minutes, don't forget to read all the problems.
